title: What time exactly is Season 5 ending?
body: I've been searching around but haven't found a solid answer.  Thanks!

replies.body:
10 hours ago (for OCE anyway, not sure if it's the same for NA).

EDIT: You know, it might help to check the news section because look what I found: http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/riot-games/announcements/2015-ranked-season-ending
I should've been more clear, sorry about that.  I know it ends at midnight, but is that pst, central or est?

**EDIT: I totally missed that you were from the North American server. If you're from NA, ignore what I wrote below, and listen to HeartVine! If you're from OCE, below is correct!**

It ended at midnight AEDT - so roughly 14 hours and 10 minutes previous to this post.  This is a bit clearer on the OCE version of the news post that HeartVine linked:
 http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/riot-games/announcements/2015-ranked-season-ending
